=== 浙江省 ===
*截止6月15日，17个县市有2059人已经被转移，79间房屋倒塌，2370公顷农田被毁<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.shanghaidaily.com/nsp/National/2011/06/16/Thousands%2Bhit%2Bby%2Brain/ |title=Thousands hit by rain |accessdate=2011-06-19 |archive-date=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130706014159/http://www.shanghaidaily.com/nsp/National/2011/06/16/Thousands%2Bhit%2Bby%2Brain/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*6月16日: 报道有2500间房屋倒塌<ref name="qiantang"/>。两个堤岸出现裂口淹没两个镇和21个村庄<ref name="FloodAlert">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/17/us-china-floods-idUSTRE75F5W220110617 |title=China allocates 35 mln yuan relief fund to flood-hit Guizhou |accessdate=2011-06-19 |archive-date=2014-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702154702/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/17/us-china-floods-idUSTRE75F5W220110617 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，导致12万人被转移<ref name="indiatimes">{{Cite news|title=120,000 evacuated in China after breach in dykes|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/120000-evacuated-in-china-after-breach-in-dykes/articleshow/8886376.cms|date=2011-06-17|accessdate=2011-06-19|archive-date=2012-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019122144/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/120000-evacuated-in-china-after-breach-in-dykes/articleshow/8886376.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*6月17日: 报道说[[钱塘江|钱塘江]]高于警戒水位2.4米，成为自1955年以来的最高水位<ref name="qiantang">{{Cite news|title=Chinese river at highest level since 1955|url=http://www.boston.com/news/world/asia/articles/2011/06/17/chinese_river_at_highest_level_since_1955/|date=2011年6月17日}}</ref>。

